condition.narrative: The Recipient shall cause MSIF to maintain, throughout Project implementation, adequate staff to support the implementation of PartA.2 of the Project, including, inter alia, a coordinator, a financial management officer, a procurement officer and anenvironmental specialist.Frequency: Continuous

The Recipient shall cause the Court of Accounts to carry out the annual financial audit of the Eligible Expenditure Program, in amanner satisfactory to the Association, and shall provide such audit financial reports to the Association, in accordance withSchedule 2 Section I.A.5 of the Legal Agreement.Frequency: Yearly

The Recipient shall ensure that MOE and MSIF carry out the Project in accordance with the provisions of the POM and shall notamend, waive or abrogate any provisions of the POM without the Association's prior approval. Frequency: Continuous
The Recipient shall ensure that no activities to be carried out under the Project involve Involuntary Resettlement per Schedule 2,Section I.C.2. Frequency: Continous
The Recipient shall ensure that no activities to be carried out under the Project involve Involuntary Resettlement. | Frequency:CONTINUOUS

The Recipient shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordance with the EMF, and thereafter ensure that the applicableEMPs are implemented, in accordance with their terms and in a manner acceptable to the Association. Except as the Associationshall otherwise agree, the Recipient shall not assign, amend, abrogate or waive the EMF or any of its provisions. | Frequency:CONTINUOUS

The Recipient shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordance with the Environmental Management Framework (EMF), andthereafter ensure that the applicable Environmental Management Plans (EMPs) are implemented, in accordance with their terms and ina manner acceptable to the Association per Schedule 2, Section I C.1 Frequency: Continuous

The Recipient through MOE shall appoint and maintain throughout implementation a project coordinator with terms of referencedescribed in the POM and acceptable to the Association. Frequency: Continuous
The Recipient, through MOE, shall appoint and maintain, throughout Project implementation, specific staff positions under theProject coordinator as further detailed in the POM.Frequency: Continuous
